sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box rgb(230, 126, 34) Customer
        participant Cust as Customer
    end
    box rgb(41, 128, 185) Spryker Checkout
        participant Cart as Cart / Checkout
        participant Split as Shipment Split (warehouse allocation)
        participant Offer as Marketplace Offer / Shipment primitives
        participant Sales as Sales / OMS
    end

    Cust->>Cart: Proceed to checkout with multi-item cart
    Cart->>Split: Determine warehouse allocation per item
    Note over Split: Items sourced from different warehouses/fulfillers<br/>(Drop Shipment modeled via Marketplace Offer + Marketplace Shipment)
    Split->>Offer: Group items into shipments per allocation
    Offer-->>Cart: One shipment per warehouse/fulfiller
    Cart->>Sales: Place order -> multiple sales shipments
    Sales->>Sales: Each shipment runs its own OMS branch
    Note over Sales: Supplier/fulfiller ships its items directly (drop shipment)
